Description: About usI now accept consignments. Now I have turned this into a hobby and I want to offer to you who may be viewing this a great experience in buying on eBay. I try to offer the buyer a lower price than most others on eBay.Refund or Replacement Policy:100% Customer satisfaction is guaranteed. I will resolve the problem to your satisfaction.I can't stress this point enough if you choose to file an open case I will have a hard time finding out who you are and your order. Therefore, wasting my time and yours. So, please message me first.Receipts are now given upon request only.There are quite a few that are paying for individual orders, if you could wait until the end of the day so that I can send you an updated invoice with all combined orders, it would be much appreciated.Thank you for bidding and have a very good day!
